<h1>Equivalent operations</h1>

<form>

<h2>Skupper CLI</h2>

<pre>$ skupper init --site-name storefront</pre>

<h2>Skupper YAML</h2>

<pre>
version: 1
site:
  name: storefront

# skupper init -f site.yaml
# skupper bundle create site.yaml bundle.tar.gz
</pre>

<h2>Skupper YAML embedded in a ConfigMap</h2>

<pre>
apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: skupper-config
  namespace: storefront
data:
  version: 1
  site:
    name: storefront

# kubectl apply -f site.yaml
</pre>

<h2>Kubernetes custom resource</h2>

<pre>
apiVersion: skupper.io/v1alpha1
kind: Site
metadata:
  name: storefront
  namespace: storefront

# kubectl apply -f site.yaml
</pre>

